java.lang.Object
org.apache.sling.scripting.sightly.impl.compiler.visitor.UniformVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class UniformVisitor extends Object implements CommandVisitor
Abstract visitor that allows to skip processing some commands.
